What is Shell?

Shell ek program hai jo user aur operating system ke beech interface ka kaam karta hai. 
Jab user terminal par koi command type karta hai, shell us command ko interpret karta hai aur 
system (kernel) ko pass karta hai. Kernel us command ko execute karta hai aur output wapas 
shell ke through user ko dikhata hai.

Popular shells:
- sh
- bash
- zsh
- ksh
- fish

Shell do tarike se use hota hai:
1. Interactive mode: Direct terminal par command chalana.
2. Scripting mode: Commands ko ek file me likhna aur script ke roop me chalana.

